      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">9.400</ph> Scope of subpart.</title>
      <body class="- topic/body ">
         <ol id="d577e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d598e10" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
							           
							This subpart-</p>
               <ol id="d577e23" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d598e16" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
									               
									Prescribes policies and procedures governing the debarment and suspension of contractors by agencies for the causes given in <xref href="9.406-2.dita#FAR_9_406_2"
                              base="i1115334"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">9.406-2</xref> and <xref href="9.407-2.dita#FAR_9_407_2"
                              base="i1115483"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">9.407-2</xref>;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d598e27" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
									               
									Provides for the listing of contractors debarred, suspended, proposed for debarment, and declared ineligible (see the definition of "ineligible" in <xref href="2.101.dita#FAR_2_101"
                              base="i1125359"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">2.101</xref>); and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d598e35" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
									               
									Sets forth the consequences of this listing.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d598e40" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
							           
							Although this subpart does cover the listing of ineligible contractors (<xref href="9.404.dita#FAR_9_404"
                        base="i1115204"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">9.404</xref>) and the effect of this listing (<xref href="9.405.dita#FAR_9_405"
                        base="i1115236"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">9.405</xref>(b)), it does not prescribe policies and procedures governing declarations of ineligibility.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
